studentship alive while pursuing professional activities by opting for RKA. Must indicate intent before late registration
date through DRC to Dean (Academics). Appropriate fees apply.
11.2 Change from M.Tech. (Regular) to M.Tech. (Part-time): After successful completion of third semester. Requires
supervisor and DRC endorsement, plus employer NOC.
